Description: Automated Test and ReTest (ATRT) Enterprise Rapid Capability develops, integrates, and deploys
novel capabilities aggregated from mature technologies to meet rapid near-term solutions to address urgent
operational needs. These capabilities are enabled through the use of virtualized systems of systems, automated
test and analysis, automated certification, rapid interface development, and field with and data collection and
edge analytics. These technologies are at the heart of the Navy's rapid capability approach, which combines
digital engineering tools with evolutionary approaches to requirements generation, operational testing, and
deployment. This process meets Fleet demands for near-term capability in a predictable and repeatable fashion.

                                                                               APID DEVELOPMENT

