Description: Funding supports the development and integration of mission system payloads, software, and
system upgrades and modifications supporting MUX Family of Systems (FoS) concepts identified within the
MUX Initial Capabilities Document (ICD). Funding also supports studies, experimentation, demonstration and
development of future MUX FoS systems.

FY 2026 Plans:
MUX will continue to support capability and payload sensor primary hardware development, NRE, capability
integration studies and design work. MUX will also support programmatic engineering, logistics and technical
requirements generation of capabilities for the MUX Family of Systems (FoS). The program will perform payload
capability improvements to include payload software as well as test required to pace evolving threats.
