FY 2026 Plans: The Space RCO will execute the Commercial Space Domain Awareness (SDA) project as a
product development effort. The congressional add will provide commercial SDA and improve real-time tracking
and response to threats in space. It will allow work towards establishing Space Force's operational framework to
enable the warfighter to protect and defend vital space assets which are essential to military victory. It will enable
and strengthen the security and resilience of national space systems allowing the Space Force to leverage
private sector investments in this vital domain. Furthermore, the congressional add will build a federated, low-
latency architecture that combines commercial and government capabilities for the real-time tracking and
analysis of objects in space.
