(CA54) Integration of Global Broadcast Services (GBS) Capabilities extends GBS secure file/video capability to commercial Satellite Communications (SATCOM)
constellations. This enables the development of a new secure On Demand portal at the GBS ground segment and the shipboard integration with Satellite Terminal
