Title: CVR Inc 2                                                                                                                            12.267           17.750      47.653
Description: Acquisition Strategy Development, Risk Reduction, and Contract Award.

FY 2026 Plans:
- Completed Acquisition Strategy Panel (ASP)
- Conduct CVRi2 Industry Day
- Completed Market Research Report (MRR) for Materiel Leader (ML) approval
- Release CVRi2 Fair Opportunity Proposal Request (FOPR)
- Initiate the Fair Opportunity Selection Process
FY 2027 Plans:
- Award delivery order incentive contracts to two qualified vendors to begin Prime Contract development work
- Hold System Requirements Review (SRR) and System Functional Review (SFR)
