D. Acquisition Strategy
The Program transitioned from a Rapid Prototyping MTA pathway to a Major Capability Acquisition (MCA) pathway. As the Milestone Decision Authority (MDA), the
PEO approved the new acquisition strategy at the Acquisition Strategy Panel (ASP) on November 25, 2025. The acquisition strategy will utilize a two vendor delivery
order that relies heavily on the implementation of Digital Materiel Management (DMM) to streamline the development process, allowing for a production competition that
delivers an advanced VLF receiver capability to the warfighter.




